[{"id":"/sicpjs/1.3.4","tag":"TITLE","body":"1.3.4  \n    \n      过程\n      函数\n    \n    作为返回值"},{"tag":"TEXT","id":"#p1","child":[{"body":"\n    上述示例演示了将\n    \n      过程\n      函数\n    作为参数传递的能力如何显著增强了我们编程语言的表达能力。我们可以通过创建返回值本身就是\n    \n      过程\n      函数\n    的\n    \n      过程。\n      函数。\n    实现更强的表达能力。\n  ","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"TEXT","id":"#p2","child":[{"body":"\n    我们可以通过再次查看在\n    section ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"1.3.3","href":"/sicpjs/1.3.3"},{"body":"结束处描述的不动点示例来说明这个想法。我们将平方根的\n    \n      过程\n      函数\n    版本公式化为不动点搜索，首先观察到\n    $\\sqrt{x}$ 是函数\n    $y\\mapsto x/y$ 的不动点。然后我们使用平均阻尼来使近似收敛。平均阻尼本身就是一种有用的通用技术。也就是说，给定一个\n    function $f$，我们考虑在 $x$ 处的值等于\n    $x$ 和 $f(x)$ 的平均值的函数。\n  ","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"TEXT","id":"#p3","child":[{"body":" \n    我们可以通过以下\n    \n      过程:\n      函数:\n    来表达平均阻尼的思想\n     ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":1,"eval":true,"prependLength":9,"program":"chap=1&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlARgHQGY0BYBQuAzAVwDsBjAFwEsB7E0AQwDcBTAJwYHMWAKADwA0oAJ4BKUAG9coGaDYsKRNvX6gA1CPFgATAG5cAX3zFy1OqADOARyIN5-cVNlyFS+n1AAqUH31HCpJS09MzsXCwA+gAmDAC2AA48BI7SsvKKyj6gALwAfIysHNz8QgQOon74oUWRMQk81rbyojwoAAwVQA","body":"function average_damp(f) {\n    return x => average(x, f(x));\n} "},{"body":"\n      \n        平均阻尼\n\t是一个过程\n      \n      \n        函数\n        ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"average_damp"},{"body":"\n    的参数为一个\n    \n      过程\n      函数","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"f"},{"body":"  并返回一个\n    \n      过程\n      函数\n      (由 lambda 生成)\n      (由 lambda 表达式生成)\n    当应用于一个数字时 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"x"},{"body":" ，生成\n    平均值  ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"x"},{"body":"  和\n    \n      (f x).\n      ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"f(x)"},{"body":".\n    例如，应用\n    \n      \n        平均阻尼\n      \n      ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"average_damp"},{"body":"\n    到  ","tag":"#text"},{"ta