y^3$","tag":"LATEX"},{"body":" \n    收敛。 另一方面，如果我们平均阻尼两次 (即，使用两次平均阻尼的\n  ","tag":"#text"},{"body":"$y\\mapsto x/y^3$","tag":"LATEX"},{"body":" ，搜索会\n    收敛。做一些实验来确定计算需要多少平均阻尼\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"body":"$n$","tag":"LATEX"},{"body":"  次方根作为基于重复平均阻尼的不动点搜索【424:17†source】。\n     ","tag":"#text"},{"body":"$y\\mapsto x/y^{n-1}$","tag":"LATEX"},{"body":" 。\n    使用这个来实现一个简单的\n    \n      过程\n      函数\n    来计算\n   ","tag":"#text"},{"body":"$n$","tag":"LATEX"},{"body":" 次方根。\n    使用\n    \n      fixed_point,\n      ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"fixed_point"},{"body":",\n      average_damp,\n      ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"average_damp"},{"body":",\n    和\n   ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"repeated"},{"body":"\n    练习 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"1.43","href":"/sicpjs/1.3.4#ex-1.43"},{"body":"中的过程\n    练习 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"1.43","href":"/sicpjs/1.3.4#ex-1.43"},{"body":"中的函数\n  。假设您需要的任何算术运算都作为原语可用。\n  ","tag":"#text"}],"solution":[{"body":"n_fold_smooth_solution\nconst dx = 0.00001;\nfunction smooth(f) {\n    return x => (f(x - dx) + f(x) + f(x + dx)) / 3;\n}\nfunction n_fold_smooth(f, n) {\n    return repeated(smooth, n)(f);\n}\n      ","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"EXERCISE","title":"Exercise 1.46","id":"#ex-1.46","child":[{"body":" \n    本章中描述的几种数值方法是一个非常通用的计算策略的实例，称为","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"EM","child":[{"body":"迭代改进","tag":"#text"}]},{"body":"。迭代改进表示，要计算某个东西，我们从初始猜测开始，测试猜测是否足够好，否则改进猜测并使用改进的方法继续该过程，以此作为新的猜测。编写一个\n    \n      过程\n      函数\n      iterative-improve\n      ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"iterative_improve"},{"body":"\n    接受两个 \n    \n      过程\n      函数\n    作为参数：一个判断猜测是否足够好的方法和一个改进猜测的方法。\n    \n      Iterative-improve\n      函数\n      ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"iterative_improve"},{"body":"\n    应返回一个其值为接受一个猜测作为参数并不断改进猜测直到它足够好的\n    \n      过程\n      函数\n    。重写   ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"sqrt"},{"body":"\n      过程\n      函数\n    section ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"1.1.7","href":"/sicpjs/1.1.7"},{"body":"和 \n    \n      fixed_point\n      ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"fixed_point"},{"body":" \n    section ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"1.3.3","href":"/sicpjs/1.3.3"},{"body":"中的\n    \n      iterative-improve\n      ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"iterative_improve"},{"body":"\n    中的\n    【4:0†cn.txt】","tag":"#text"}],"solution":[{"body":"iterative_improve\nfunction iterative_improve(is_good_enough, improve) {\n    function iterate(guess) {\n        return is_good_enough(guess)\n               ? guess\n               : iterate(improve(guess));\n    }\n    return iterate;\n}\t\t    \n\texample_1.46_1\nfunction sqrt(x) {\n    return iterative_improve(y => is_good_enough(y, x), \n                             y => improve(y, x))(1);\n}\n\nsqrt(49);\n\t","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"DISPLAYFOOTNOTE","id":"#footnote-1","count":1,"href":"/sicpjs/1.3.4#footnote-link-1","child":[{"body":"\n      \n\t注意这是一个运算符本身是\n\t\n\t一个组合。练习 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"1.4","href":"/sicpjs/1.1.6#ex-1.4"},{"body":"已经展示了形成这种组合的能力，但那只是一个玩具示例。这里我们开始看到这种组合的实际需求—当应用一个过程时，该过程是由高阶过程返回的值获得的。\n      \n      \n\t注意这是一个函数表达式本身是\n\t\n\t一个应用。练习 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"1.4","href":"/sicpjs/1.1.6#ex-1.4"},{"body":"已经展示了形成这种应用的能力，但那只是一个玩具示例。这里我们开始看到这种应用的实际需要—当应用一个函数时，该函数是由高阶函数返回的值获得的。\n      ","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"DISPLAYFOOTNOTE","id":"#footnote-2","count":2,"href":"/sicpjs/1.3.4#footnote-link-2","child":[{"body":"参见练习 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"1.45","href":"/sicpjs/1.3.4#ex-1.45"},{"body":" \n    以获得进一步的推广。","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"DISPLAYFOOTNOTE","id":"#footnote-3","count":3,"href":"/sicpjs/1.3.4#footnote-link-3","child":[{"body":"初等微积分书籍通常用逼近序列 $x_{n+1}=x_n-g(x_n)/Dg(x_n)$ 来描述牛顿法。拥有描述过程的语言并使用不动点的概念可以简化方法的描述。","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"DISPLAYFOOTNOTE","id":"#footnote-4","count":4,"href":"/sicpjs/1.3.4#footnote-link-4","child":[{"body":"牛顿法并不总是收敛到一个解，但可以证明，在有利情况下，每次迭代都会使逼近解的数字位数加倍。在这种情况下， \n    \n    牛顿法将比半区间法收敛得快得多。","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"DISPLAYFOOTNOTE","id":"#footnote-5","count":5,"href":"/sicpjs/1.3.4#footnote-link-5","child":[{"body":"对于寻找平方根，牛顿法从任何起始点快速收敛到正确的解决方案。","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"DISPLAYFOOTNOTE","id":"#footnote-6","count":6,"href":"/sicpjs/1.3.4#footnote-link-6","child":[{"body":"编程语言元素的一等公民概念由英国计算机科学家\n    \n    Christopher Strachey (1916–1975) 提出。","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"DISPLAYFOOTNOTE","id":"#footnote-7","count":7,"href":"/sicpjs/1.3.4#footnote-link-7","child":[{"body":"我们将在引入数据结构后，在第 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"2","href":"/sicpjs/2"},{"body":"章中看到这一点的例子。","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"DISPLAYFOOTNOTE","id":"#footnote-8","count":8,"href":"/sicpjs/1.3.4#footnote-link-8","child":[{"body":"一等\n    \n      过程\n      函数\n    主要的实现代价在于允许\n    \n      过程\n      函数\n    作为值返回，需要为\n    \n      过程'的自由变量\n      函数'的自由名称\n    保留存储空间，即使\n    \n      过程\n      函数\n    没有执行。\n    \n      \n        在我们将在\n        section ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"4.1","href":"/sicpjs/4.1"},{"body":"中研究的 Scheme 实现中，这些变量存储在过程的\n      \n      \n        在我们将在\n        section ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"4.1","href":"/sicpjs/4.1"},{"body":"中研究的 JavaScript 实现中，这些名称存储在函数的\n       环境中。","tag":"#text"}]}]